com.authlete.cose

Class COSEKeyBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.authlete.cose.COSEKeyBuilder

  • public class COSEKeyBuilder
extends Object
    A utility to build an instance of COSEKey or its subclass (e.g. COSEOKPKey and COSEEC2Key).
    Since:
    1.1
    See Also:
    RFC 9052, 7. Key Objects, IANA: COSE Key Common Parameters, IANA: COSE Key Type Parameters, IANA: COSE Key Types, IANA: COSE Elliptic Curves
